<P>
 Eight true freshmen have been getting playing time at UCLA this season and 
one, cornerback Javelin Guidry, is starting. 
</P>
<P>
 The other seven are defensive lineman Vae Tata, nose guard Danjuan Magee, wide 
receiver Jim McElroy, safety Shaun Williams, safety Glenn Thompkins, fullback 
Greg Ford and cornerback Aaron Rocques. 
</P>
<P>
 There are only 14 scholarship seniors, including punter Darren Schager and 
long snapper Chris Andersen, who were walk-ons who earned scholarships. 
</P>
