<P>
EAST VENTURA COUNTY FOCUS: THOUSAND OAKS; FRIENDS OF LIBRARY SPONSOR BOOK SALE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By TRACY WILSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Friends of the Thousand Oaks Library will hold a three-day book sale at 
the main library beginning today and continuing through the weekend. Hardcover 
books will sell for 75 cents each, and paperbacks for 25 cents. Today and 
Saturday, children's books will be 10 to 50 cents, and a special 10-cent 
"clean-up sale" will be held Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 The used-book sale will begin tonight at 6 p.m. and close at 9 p.m. The sale 
will continue Saturday from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. and Sunday from 1 p.m. to 3 p.m. 
TRACY WILSON 
