<TEXT>
<P>
 In the Garden Grove League: 
</P>
<P>
 Lynn Wu takes singles title -- La Quinta's Lynn Wu defeated Tien Nguyen of 
Santiago, 6-1, 6-0, to win the singles title. 
</P>
<P>
 Yee-Luu and Lyly Tran of Los Amigos took the doubles title with a 6-2, 6-4 
victory over Santiago's Yvonne Vu and Mai-Uien Huynh. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Pacific Coast League: 
</P>
<P>
 Bray takes singles title -- Top-seeded Michelle Bray of Laguna Beach defeated 
