Charmin display for the occasion that read: 'For your other throne room.' " 
</P>
<P>
 Comedy writer Alan Ray, on cutbacks at Hershey's chocolate: "Layoff notices 
were a bit terse. Workers in the bite-sized candy division were told to kiss 
off." 
