<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOTRE DAME'S DIXON COMMITS TO USD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KENNEDY COSGROVE 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Maggie Dixon, a Notre Dame High girls' basketball player, has committed to the 
University of San Diego and will sign with the Toreros during the early signing 
period that begins November 9. 
</P>
<P>
 Dixon, a 6-foot-1 senior, averaged 11.7 points and 10.3 rebounds last season 
