<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110494-0219 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 095321 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 4, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
